&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Data Visualization Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; is a specialist dedicated to transforming complex, raw data into clear, actionable, and visually compelling narratives. This role is centered on &lt;strong&gt;Tableau mastery&lt;/strong&gt;, requiring an individual who can not only build interactive dashboards but also architect the data models that power them. The Analyst will work closely with client strategists to define KPIs, identify trends, and communicate insights that drive strategic decision-making. While the core focus is technical visualization, an understanding of marketing and media metrics is highly valued to support our agency’s data storytelling efforts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ignore-global-css&quot;&gt;Essential Duties and Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ignore-global-css&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ignore-global-css&quot;&gt;(Other duties may be assigned)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expert Dashboard Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the design, creation, and maintenance of interactive, user-friendly, and high-impact reports in &lt;strong&gt;Tableau&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring all visualizations meet brand standards and user needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Analysis &amp;amp; Modeling:&lt;/strong&gt; Clean, organize, and analyze datasets from disparate sources to identify critical trends and patterns. Use &lt;strong&gt;SQL&lt;/strong&gt; to extract and manipulate data for efficient reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Data Storytelling:&lt;/strong&gt; Translate technical findings into visual formats (graphs, charts, heatmaps) that provide clear, actionable recommendations for executive and technical stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirement Gathering:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as a bridge between technical teams and business units, working directly with stakeholders to define reporting requirements and establish relevant Key Performance Indicators (KPIs).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Automation:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify and implement opportunities for automation within the data reporting lifecycle to increase efficiency and reduce manual data handling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quality Assurance:&lt;/strong&gt; Perform rigorous data validation and testing to ensure the accuracy and integrity of all dashboards and reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ad-Hoc Reporting:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide rapid-response data analysis and visualization to support urgent business questions or client requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
